data.description: Welcome to the highly sought after DRIFTWOOD ESTATES neighborhood! This beautiful BRICK home offers an extensive front yard with plenty of driveway space for parking. Enter the home into a spacious foyer that leads to the OPEN CONCEPT floor plan.  Feel right at home in the inviting and spacious gathering area, encompassing the living room,dining area,and kitchen featuring granite counters. The Spacious Owner's Suite features a Trey ceiling. The Master bath features a Double vanity with granite countertops, garden tub and separate shower. Oversize backyard backs up to preservation area. **Neighborhood also offers large playground area with basketball courts, tennis courts and open green space. Take a dip in the community pool within walking distance of the home
